You're having an affair.

9
00:01:19,704 --> 00:01:21,637
You seduced me.

10
00:01:21,637 --> 00:01:24,404
I told you not to, but you kept at it,

11
00:01:24,404 --> 00:01:27,371
singing around me,

12
00:01:27,371 --> 00:01:30,204
bringing me flowers and such.

13
00:01:31,004 --> 00:01:35,737
I started wavering, and then fell for you.

14
00:01:35,737 --> 00:01:37,470
Wait a minute.

15
00:01:37,470 --> 00:01:40,204
Why are you blaming me?

16
00:01:40,204 --> 00:01:42,837
I didn't do anything major.

17
00:01:42,837 --> 00:01:45,537
