24
00:02:05,404 --> 00:02:07,371
Where are you going?

25
00:02:07,371 --> 00:02:10,304
You're having a birthday party
with your new lover.

26
00:02:12,137 --> 00:02:14,404
Today's Kang Gyeong Jun's birthday.

27
00:02:14,404 --> 00:02:17,737
Yes. He's quite a celebrity at the hospital.

28
00:02:17,737 --> 00:02:19,304
This looks good.

29
00:02:19,304 --> 00:02:19,937
Enjoy.

30
00:02:19,937 --> 00:02:21,837
[Happy Birthday KKJ]

31
00:02:22,804 --> 00:02:24,837
KKJ?

32
00:02:24,837 --> 00:02:26,737
Kang Gyeong Jun?

33
00:02:27,837 --> 00:02:30,770
If he weren't in a coma, I would've
thought it was the same person.

34
00:02:39,271 --> 00:02:41,004
Dr. Seo,

35
00:02:43,237 --> 00:02:44,670
hello.

36
00:02:44,670 --> 00:02:47,537
I'm Lee Se Yeong, Gyeong Jun's
primary care physician.

37
00:02:47,537 --> 00:02:49,304
So you're Yun Jae's friend

38
00:02:49,304 --> 00:02:52,570
who knows about Gyeong Jun.

39
00:02:54,670 --> 00:02:57,904
Did someone come by looking
to take Gyeong Jun away?

40
00:02:57,904 --> 00:02:59,637
I don't know.

41
00:03:00,104 --> 00:03:01,470
Where's Dr. Lee?

42
00:03:01,470 --> 00:03:03,237
She went that way.

43
00:03:08,570 --> 00:03:12,004
From now on, discuss anything that
has to do with Gyeong Jun with me.

44
00:03:12,004 --> 00:03:13,237
Sure.

45
00:03:13,237 --> 00:03:17,171
You are his father after all.

46
00:03:19,371 --> 00:03:21,970
I will call you from time to time
to keep you posted.

47
00:03:21,970 --> 00:03:24,004
Thank you.

48
00:03:26,171 --> 00:03:28,603
Gyeong Jun's father?

49
00:03:35,037 --> 00:03:36,937
You really do come by every day.

50
00:03:36,937 --> 00:03:40,204
Of course. Gyeong Jun's family to me.

51
00:04:01,037 --> 00:04:02,737
Excuse me.

52
00:04:13,804 --> 00:04:18,304
But you're Dr. Seo Yun Jae's father.

53
00:04:18,804 --> 00:04:20,904
You are...

54
00:04:25,104 --> 00:04:29,404
Are you Gyeong Jun's father?

55
00:04:29,737 --> 00:04:31,670
♪ Happy birthday ♪

56
00:04:31,670 --> 00:04:34,937
♪ Dear Gyeong Jun ♪

57
00:04:34,937 --> 00:04:37,004
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

58
00:04:37,004 --> 00:04:38,737
Happy birthday.

59
00:04:38,737 --> 00:04:40,503
Happy birthday.

60
00:04:44,503 --> 00:04:45,704
Are you happy that

61
00:04:45,704 --> 00:04:48,271
you insisted on coming to a place like this?

62
00:04:48,770 --> 00:04:50,438
This is the perfect place for a kid
to have his birthday party.

63
00:04:51,371 --> 00:04:53,304
Are you kidding me?

64
00:04:53,304 --> 00:04:55,371
