71
00:05:11,804 --> 00:05:13,404
Were you trying to run away

72
00:05:13,404 --> 00:05:15,171
because you were fearful
of what might lie ahead?

73
00:05:15,171 --> 00:05:17,704
You said you were reckless
because you were a kid, right?

74
00:05:17,704 --> 00:05:19,438
But I'm not. I have a lot to worry about.

75
00:05:19,438 --> 00:05:22,338
Kick those worries aside as things unfold.

76
00:05:22,970 --> 00:05:25,271
