77
00:05:26,104 --> 00:05:28,637
I'll give you the strength.

78
00:05:28,637 --> 00:05:32,704
I'll do more than just little nice things.
They'll be major nice things.

79
00:05:33,204 --> 00:05:35,570
You are Gyeong Jun's father, right?

80
00:05:36,603 --> 00:05:41,171
It was you who had wanted
to meet me about Gyeong Jun.

81
00:05:42,204 --> 00:05:46,904
Does this mean Gyeong Jun
is Dr. Seo's younger brother?

82
00:05:46,904 --> 00:05:49,404
Please don't tell Yun Jae

83
00:05:49,404 --> 00:05:51,637
and put him in an awkward position.

84
00:05:51,637 --> 00:05:56,037
Who's more important to you,
Dr. Seo or Gyeong Jun?

85
00:05:57,537 --> 00:06:00,071
Dr. Seo's more important to you, right?

86
00:06:00,071 --> 00:06:02,770
That's why you've been trying
to keep Gyeong Jun a secret.

87
00:06:02,770 --> 00:06:05,804
I'm sorry, but I have my reasons.

88
00:06:05,804 --> 00:06:07,804
I don't care about your reasons.

89
00:06:07,804 --> 00:06:10,237
Gyeong Jun's the only thing
that matters to me.

90
00:06:10,237 --> 00:06:13,204
What you did to Gyeong Jun was wrong.

91
00:06:13,204 --> 00:06:15,537
You're bad.

92
00:06:17,171 --> 00:06:20,237
Gyeong Jun will be sad if he finds out.

93
00:06:24,237 --> 00:06:27,837
I thought things would be better
if he found his father,

94
00:06:27,837 --> 00:06:29,637
but things have only gotten
more complicated.

95
00:06:37,004 --> 00:06:38,770
[Roundtrip Ticket to the Moon A-1]

96
00:06:38,770 --> 00:06:40,104
Give me your cell phone.
[Touch to Share Photo]

97
00:06:51,004 --> 00:06:52,570
What's this?

98
00:06:53,537 --> 00:06:56,338
Roundtrip ticket to the moon?

99
