It'll probably be possible in about 20 years.

100
00:06:58,503 --> 00:06:59,770
I'm sure it's beautiful there.

101
00:06:59,770 --> 00:07:01,537
How do you know such
a thing will be possible?

102
00:07:01,537 --> 00:07:04,237
Did we know 20 years ago
we'd have something like this?

103
00:07:05,371 --> 00:07:08,104
I'm sure it'll happen. We'll go together.

104
00:07:08,104 --> 00:07:11,637
We can listen to the Seo Taiji and Boys
40th anniversary album.

105
00:07:11,637 --> 00:07:15,071
The person who guesses the winner
of the 2034 World Cup gets the tickets.

106
00:07:15,071 --> 00:07:18,071
You can check to see if the Great Wall

107
00:07:18,071 --> 00:07:20,137
is visible from the moon.

108
00:07:20,137 --> 00:07:22,503
And I'll look for my family on the moon.

109
00:07:22,970 --> 00:07:28,204
You'll be so relieved I seduced you,

110
00:07:28,737 --> 00:07:32,404
and I'll give you the 874th kiss.

111
00:07:34,037 --> 00:07:36,570
Look forward to the majorly
nice things I'll do for you,

112
00:07:36,570 --> 00:07:38,670
and hang in there, Gil Teacher.

113
00:07:38,670 --> 00:07:40,837
Are you going to give up
on a trip to the moon?

114
00:07:43,537 --> 00:07:45,104
[Roundtrip Ticket to the Moon A-1]

115
00:07:48,570 --> 00:07:50,704
I'm but a common earthling.

116
00:07:50,704 --> 00:07:52,804
I have no business in outer space.

117
00:07:52,804 --> 00:07:55,704
I'd just want to jump into
a blackhole and disappear.

118
00:07:55,704 --> 00:07:58,870
You said you wanted to drown
in the ocean earlier...

119
00:07:58,870 --> 00:08:00,104
Then how about a submarine adventure?

120
00:08:00,104 --> 00:08:01,804
That's enough.

121
00:08:02,503 --> 00:08:04,237
- In about 15 years...
- Stop it.

122
00:08:05,071 --> 00:08:07,104
I'm just doing my best to seduce you.

123
00:08:07,104 --> 00:08:08,570
Hang in there,

124
00:08:08,570 --> 00:08:10,004
and hold onto me.

125
00:08:16,904 --> 00:08:18,503
Hang on.

126
00:08:19,503 --> 00:08:20,937
Why?

127
00:08:20,937 --> 00:08:24,570
