until she gets what she wants.

243
00:15:15,704 --> 00:15:19,704
No one would mind a pretty express train
like her charging at them.

244
00:15:19,704 --> 00:15:21,037
You two look good together.

245
00:15:21,037 --> 00:15:23,937
Jang Mary is very pretty.

246
00:15:23,937 --> 00:15:26,104
There are oil deposits in her father's land.

247
00:15:26,104 --> 00:15:28,804
A full tour of his property takes 30 minutes.

248
00:15:28,804 --> 00:15:31,137
- By car?
- By helicopter.

249
00:15:32,071 --> 00:15:35,237
