00:58:17,770 --> 00:58:21,470
and never fall for Gyeong Jun.

803
00:58:21,470 --> 00:58:23,837
Stay true to your word.

804
00:58:26,438 --> 00:58:28,670
I...

805
00:58:29,438 --> 00:58:31,503
I just can't...

806
00:58:31,503 --> 00:58:34,737
If you can't do it, you can pretend.

807
00:58:35,870 --> 00:58:40,304
If you insist on being selfish
and stay with Gyeong Jun,

808
00:58:40,304 --> 00:58:42,503
both Gyeong Jun

809
00:58:43,970 --> 00:58:47,503
and Dr. Seo will die.

810
00:58:51,970 --> 00:58:55,237
I...

811
00:58:55,237 --> 00:58:59,371
I would lie for Gyeong Jun.

812
00:59:01,204 --> 00:59:06,037
You can do the same and pretend.

813
00:59:07,570 --> 00:59:12,338
Please tell Gyeong Jun

814
00:59:12,338 --> 00:59:14,404
to return to his own body.

815
01:00:56,537 --> 01:00:59,837
Did you

816
01:00:59,837 --> 01:01:02,404
really know everything?

817
01:01:04,104 --> 01:01:06,304
Yes.

818
01:01:07,970 --> 01:01:10,770
Then why

819
01:01:10,770 --> 01:01:13,271
did you keep it from me?

820
01:01:23,104 --> 01:01:26,371
You did it because you didn't
want me to worry, right?

821
01:01:31,970 --> 01:01:35,204
I'm

822
01:01:36,237 --> 01:01:40,137
so angry and scared.

823
01:01:44,537 --> 01:01:48,171
Please hold my hand.

824
01:02:08,438 --> 01:02:11,137
I...

825
01:02:11,137 --> 01:02:14,438
I can't hold your hand.

826
01:02:17,037 --> 01:02:19,870
Yun Jae comes first.

827
01:02:22,670 --> 01:02:25,870
I'm going back to him.

828
01:02:31,271 --> 01:02:34,271
10:10 has come and gone,

829
01:02:35,503 --> 01:02:38,870
and I've come to my senses.

830
01:02:42,637 --> 01:02:45,970
Gyeong Jun,

831
01:02:46,837 --> 01:02:50,004
please save Yun Jae,

832
01:02:52,970 --> 01:02:55,570
and

833
01:02:58,904 --> 01:03:01,438
go back to your body.

834
01:03:17,071 --> 01:03:22,037
If that's what you want...

835
01:03:56,271 --> 01:03:57,737
[Big]

836
01:03:58,004 --> 01:04:00,904
Promise me you will put Gyeong Jun first.

837
01:04:00,904 --> 01:04:03,104
She said she had known everything

838
01:04:03,104 --> 01:04:04,804
and only stayed with me to save Yun Jae.

839
01:04:04,804 --> 01:04:06,204
Did you tell her

840
01:04:06,204 --> 01:04:08,570
you loved her and had her
give you a baby for your son?

841
01:04:08,570 --> 01:04:09,438
Yun Jae.

842
01:04:09,438 --> 01:04:11,470
Is that how you got her
to have Kang Gyeong Jun?

843
01:04:11,470 --> 01:04:12,637
It was me.

844
01:04:12,637 --> 01:04:15,770
There was nothing I wouldn't do for you.

845
01:04:15,770 --> 01:04:17,004
Stop it.

846
01:04:17,004 --> 01:04:18,470
Then tell me how you really feel.

847
01:04:18,470 --> 01:04:20,470
Tell me I should do whatever
I want to in this wretched situation.

848
01:04:20,470 --> 01:04:22,271
Tell me I come first no matter what.

849
01:04:22,271 --> 01:04:25,071
Stop me by telling me you can let go
of everything else because I come first.

850
01:04:25,071 --> 01:04:27,570
I get the feeling it will be 10:10
for me for the rest of my life.

851
01:04:27,570 --> 01:04:29,304
Find me a house for long-term rental

852
01:04:29,304 --> 01:04:31,371
in Palos Verdes, California.

853
01:04:31,371 --> 01:04:35,071
I won't let them use me
like they used my mom.
